Sorry Blizz <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uwilrowe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wilrowe</A> at: 1/16/02 10:57:56 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ulleauaric.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lleauaric</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/16/02 11:01:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=804.topic&index=273>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.att.net/~ashleyellinor/images/photoindex/deniroguns.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Things you do after leaving a guild...</span><hr size=1> Chaincasting sunstrike &gt; all<br>
